{"tid":1849254,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何栢良倡派警尋留港湖北武漢人","createTime":"2020-01-29T03:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T03:11:51.000Z","uid":221211,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7d4ecd248b776f652552b4b9483a9298cd2e655b","tid":1849254,"uid":221211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:06:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2363381/何栢良倡派警尋留港湖北武漢人\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2363381%2F%E4%BD%95%E6%A0%A2%E8%89%AF%E5%80%A1%E6%B4%BE%E8%AD%A6%E5%B0%8B%E7%95%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B9%96%E5%8C%97%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E4%BA%BA&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Jibpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=2e195365\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2363381/何栢良倡派警尋留港湖北武漢人</a><br />\n<br />\n香港大學感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良表示，現時市民與新型冠狀病毒零距離，擔心若廣東省爆發第二波疫情、出現社區爆發的話，本港會「守不住」。<br />\n<br />\n他又指政府現時採取的措施明顯不足夠，強調全面封關不代表暫停所有交通工具，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">建議仿傚澳門做法派警方到各酒店，找出仍留港武漢或湖北人，安排隔離治療或者返回內地。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n他表明自己不呼籲醫護人員罷工，但明白和理解醫護人員有相關訴求，建議如有醫護在道德上感到矛盾，可考慮辭職。"},{"pid":"00a6388739eac5048499d826cf23059455b85e96","tid":1849254,"uid":240374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:10:42.000Z","msg":"大啲醫護？"},{"pid":"3da8fb9125987f977087f78151536a115486c663","tid":1849254,"uid":259813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"00a6388739eac5048499d826cf23059455b85e96","tid":1849254,"uid":240374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:10:42.000Z","msg":"大啲醫護？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:11:51.000Z","msg":"應該大唔到<br />\n醫護去邊都有人要，移民個個國家搶住收"}]}